Goal section
* 11111111, 00011111, 10001111 and 00100011 are not variables. You may format them as <<bold>>.

Input section
* There should be a brief description of the variables here, e.g.
   • the starting state
   • the number of bits
   • the clock toggles
* You may format H, L, 0 and 9 as {{constants}} and remove the quotation marks around the characters.

Output section
* You may format 0 and 1 as {{constants}}.

Constraints section
* You may format H, L, 0 and 9 as {{constants}} and remove the quotation marks around the characters.

Thanks.
Fixed, thank you for the input!
